parameters: I came to check on you. Are you still alive?
You're the one showing your face around here, huh?
Could it be you've started to miss me?\I[12]

I've had my fair share of dealings with you; it would be
troubling if you died.

I even brought you food, would it be alright if I just left
without giving it to you?
Oh, for real? That's much appreciated.

Going through all this trouble, you must have feelings for
me, huh?

damn hot.\I[12]

could hear a woman's moans of ecstasy.\I[12]

the woman who was moaning like mad.\I[12]
